Iterambere ry'icyorezo cya Coronavirus (COVID-19) mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Afurika y'u Burayi/Ibihugu by'ubukungu n'u Bwongereza kuva ku itariki ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus (COVID-19) kigenda gitera imbere mu bihugu by'umuryango w'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Afurika y'ubukungu, kandi u Bwongereza bwagaragaje ko mu gihe kiri mu byiciro bitandukanye bitewe n'igihugu, icyorezo cya COVID-19 kigenda gitera imbere mu buryo bwihuse mu bihugu byose.
Dushingiye ku byaranze Ubutaliyani, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi bikwiye kurushaho kwitegura umubare wiyongereye w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bazaba bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane.
Ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, hari inkuru z'indwara y'ibihaha ya Ramrai, iyo nyirabayazana wayo akaba atari we uzwi, zavuzwe mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ku itariki ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'Ubushinwa Gishinzwe Genzura no Gukumira Indwara cyatangaje ko ikoranabuhanga rishya ry'agakoko gatera indwara ya Coronavirusi (COV-2), ari yo virusi ya Coronavirusi ya 2 y'umugera w'indwara z'ubwonko zandura mu buryo bukomeye (SARS-CoV-2).
Kuva icyo gihe, indwara ziterwa n'indwara ya SARS-CoV-2 ziswe Coronavirus (COVID-19).
Kugeza ubu, hari ibimenyetso bigaragaza ko 80% by'abanduye COVID-19 bafite ubwandu bworoheje, ni ukuvuga ubwandu bw'indwara zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero, bafite cyangwa badafite ubwandu bw'ibihaha, kandi abenshi muri abo barwayi barakira.
Mu bantu 14 ku ijana barwaye COVID-19, barwara indwara zikomeye zikeneye kuruhuka mu bitaro, mu gihe abandi 6% barwara indwara zikomeye zikeneye kwitabwaho cyane.
Umubare w'abarwayi bapfa bavurirwa mu bitaro kubera COVID-19 ni 4%.
Muri iki cyifuzo, twashyize mu gaciro ibipimo by'ibimenyetso by'ubwiyongere bw'icyorezo cya COVID-19 muri buri gihugu cy'umuryango w'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/uburasirazuba bw'u Burayi (EU/EEA) n'ubwongereza, maze tugereranya na Hubei, Ubushinwa.
Twagereranyije umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 muri iyi minsi mu bihugu by'umuryango w'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Afurika y'u Burayi/Afurika y'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza n'uw'abanduye mu Butaliyani hagati ya 31 Mutarama na 15 Werurwe 2020.
Ibibazo by'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 mu bihugu by'umuryango w'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Afurika y'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza.
Nyuma yo kwigarurira Ubushinwa, icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyakomeje gukwirakwira, kandi icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyakwirakwira ku isi hose muri iki gihe, kigenda giherekeje inzira y'u Bushinwa.
Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe 2020, umuyobozi mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo cyandura ku isi hose.
Mu nyandiko ya 5 ya Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri n'abandi batangaje ko COVID-19 yemejwe na EU mu buryo bwa mbere, hashingiwe ku makuru y'ibanze y'umuryango w'abibumbye wita ku buzima.
Mu bihugu by'u Burayi/Afurika y'Ubukungu, abantu batatu ba mbere bavuzwe ko banduye, bavuzwe n'Ubufaransa ku wa 24 Mutarama 2020 ku bantu bagarutse mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020, COVID-19 imaze kugaragara mu bihugu 30 by'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Afurika y'u Burayi/Afurika y'u Burayi/Afurika y'u Burayi/Ubwongereza, aho hagati y'itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 n'uwo munsi hazaba hari abantu 39,768 banduye iyi ndwara, n'abantu 1,727 bapfuye, aho abanduye 17,750 n'abapfuye 1,441 bakaba baturutse mu Butaliyani honyine.
Twemere umubare w'abantu bose banduye COVID-19 n'ibyabaye muri rusange.
Mu kigo cy'u Burayi gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (ECDC), imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 batangajwe mu bihugu byose ku isi, hakoreshejwe amakuru y'ibanze nk'ibiro by'ubuzima, inzego z'ubuzima z'ibihugu n'uturere, n'umuryango w'abibumbye wita ku buzima, iherutse kuvugururwa buri munsi saa munani za mu gitondo.
Ibi byose bikoreshwa mu gupima icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu bihugu by'umuryango w'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Afurika y'ubukungu, kimwe n'u Bwongereza, no kugereranya ibi byose n'ibya Italy.
Mu rwego rwo guhagararira icyorezo cya COVID-19, twagerageje kugenzura ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyakomeje kwiyongera mu minsi 14 bitewe n'uko icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatangiye kugenda mu bihugu by'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Afurika y'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi (EU/EEA) no mu Bwongereza hagati ya tariki ya 1 Mutarama kugeza tariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Twagaragaje kandi umubare w'abanduye mu gihugu cyose bamenyekanye ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020 saa munani za mu gitondo ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani hagati ya 31 Mutarama na 15 Werurwe 2020.
