Ibi bikorwa bikorwa mu bihe byambere by'ubwandu, bigamije gukurikirana no kwiherera abanduye, ndetse no gushyiraho izindi ngamba zo kugenzura, gukwirakwiza no gukingira kugira ngo indwara ihagarike gukwirakwira ku baturage bose.
Iyo indwara idashobora guhagarara, imihati ikomeza kugabanuka: hashyirwaho ingamba zo kugabanya ikwirakwira no kugabanya ingaruka ku buryo bw'ubuzima n'imibereho y'abantu.
Hari igihe umuntu ashobora kuba afite ikibazo cy'uburwayi, akumva ko hari icyo atakoze.
Gufata ingamba zo kwirinda icyorezo mu kugabanya umubare w'abanduye ku gitsina ku kigero kiri munsi ya kimwe cya kabiri cy'ubutegetsi, ni cyo gituma ikwirakwira ry'indwara z'ubwandu rigerageza kugabanya umubare munini w'abanduye uzwi ku izina rya "square line".
Iyi gahunda igabanya ibyago byo kugira ibibazo by'ubuzima kandi igaha igihe kinini cyo gukora inkingo n'ubuvuzi.
Ibitekerezo by'abaturage bigamije guhungabanya uburwayi, kugabanya uburwayi, gufunga amashuri no guhagarika amateraniro manini. Abaturage bashyizeho gahunda yo gushishikariza abantu kwakira no kwifatanya muri ibi bitekerezo. Imirimo myinshi igamije kurwanya iki cyorezo yabaye mu Bushinwa, ubwo uburwayi bw'iki cyorezo bwari bwarabaye bukomeye cyane, nk'imyuzure mu mijyi yose no guhagarika ingendo.
Ibihugu byinshi byemeje ingamba zigamije kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'iyi virusi.
Koreya y'Epfo yakoze igenzura rikomeye no guhagarika abantu ku giti cyabo ku buryo bw'ibanze, kandi itanga itangazo ku bimenyetso by'abantu banduye.
Singapore yahaye inkunga y'amafaranga abanduye, ibyangombwa by'ubuhinduzi, ndetse ikashyiraho ibihano bikomeye ku batagendera ku mategeko.
Taiwan yongeye gukora ibipfukisho by'amaso no gushyiraho ibihano ku kugura ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi. Ingingo z'u Bwongereza na Amerika zigaragaza ko kugabanya (kugabanya ariko ntibuhagarike ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo) no kugabanya (kugabanya ubwandu) bigira ibibazo bikomeye.
Ingamba nziza zo kugabanya bishobora kugabanya umubare w'abapfapfa mu bihumbi bibiri na bibiri, ariko bikomeza guhitana abantu babarirwa mu bihumbi amagana, kandi n'ikoranabuhanga ry'ubuzima rikaba ryarasenyutse.
Gushyiraho ingamba bishobora guhitamo no gukoreshwa, kandi bigomba gukorwa mugihe virusi ikwirakwira ku bantu (cyangwa kugeza igihe hari urukingo niba hari mbere), igihe ikwirakwira ryigaragaza vuba igihe ingamba zishyirwa mu bikorwa.
Kugabanya ingamba zo kwirinda iki cyorezo mu gihe kirekire byateje akaga mu rwego rw'imibereho n'ubukungu.
Nta muti wihariye wa virusi yemewe ku COVID-19, ariko hari ingufu zikomeje gukorwa, harimo no kugerageza imiti iriho.
Gukoresha imiti yo kugabanya ubukana, kunywa amazi menshi no kuruhuka bishobora kugabanya ibimenyetso.
Bitewe n'ubukana, imiti ya Oxygen, imiti y'umurava n'ubufasha bwo guhumeka bishobora gukenerwa.
Iyo umuntu afashwe n'ibikoresho by'imiti, ashobora gutuma ibintu birushaho kuzamba.
Ingingo nyinshi z'ibanze zategetswe kuvurwa kw'indwara ziterwa n'izindi virusi ziri gukorwaho ubushakashatsi kugira ngo zikoreshwe mu kuvura COVID-19.
OMS kandi yemeza ko uburyo bumwe na bumwe bwo kuvura bw'umwimerere no mu rugo bushobora gukiza ibimenyetso byatewe na SARS-CoV-19.
Guteza imbere ubushobozi no guhangana n'ikibazo cy'ubuzima ku barwayi ba COVID-19 byasobanuwe n'umuryango w'abibumbye wita ku buzima nk'ingamba zo guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
ECDC na WHO mu Burayi byatangaje impamvu za mbere zituma ibitaro n'ubuvuzi bikomeza guhinduranya umutungo ku rwego rwinshi, harimo gushyira imbaraga mu bikorwa ibikorwa byo gupima COVID-19, guhagarika gahunda zo guhitamo igihe bishoboka, guhagarika no kwiherera abarwayi ba COVID-19, no kongera ubushobozi bwo kwita ku buvuzi bwihariye binyuze mu gutoza abakozi no kongera umubare w'ibikoresho byo guhumeka no kuryamisha.
Hari ibitekerezo bitandukanye ku kuntu icyorezo cya mbere (cyitwa icyorezo cy'indwara) gishobora gutangira.
Icyorezo cya mbere cy'iyi virusi, kizwi nka virusi nshya, gishobora kuba cyarabonetse ku itariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Mu kwezi kumwe gusa, umubare w'abanduye virusi itera SIDA mu mujyi wa Hobi wariyongereye cyane.
Abenshi muri abo barwayi bari bafitanye isano n'isoko ry'ibiribwa byo mu nyanja rya Huanan, na ryo ryatangaga ibinyabuzima, kandi hari ibimenyetso byavugaga ko iyi virusi yavuye ku bwoko bw'inyamaswa muri izo nyamaswa, cyangwa se ko ishobora kuvugwa ko yavuye ku nyamaswa. Abanduye indwara y'ibihaha zitazwi, bagenzurwa ku itariki ya 26 Ukuboza, kandi bavurwa na Dr. Zhang Jixian mu bitaro by'ubuvuzi bw'ibanze byo mu ntara ya Hubei, aho yashyikirije ibigo by'ubuvuzi n'ubudahangarwa mu mujyi wa Wuhan ku itariki ya 27 Ukuboza.
Ku itariki ya 30 Ukuboza, umuganga wo mu bitaro bya Wuhan Central Hospital yamenyesheje abakozi be ko hari virusi SARs nka coronavirus.
Abaganga umunani barimo Li Wenliang, bacyuriwe na polisi kubera gukwirakwiza ibinyoma, naho undi witwa Ai Fen yagaragaye ahamwa n'ibyaha byo guteza imidugararo.
Komisiyo y'ubuzima ya Wuhan yaje gushyira ahagaragara itangazo ku wa 31 Ukuboza, maze itangira kubimenyesha Umuryango w'Abibumbye wita ku buzima.
