Urugero, Beijing yategetse ko abanyamahanga bose binjira mu mujyi bahabwa iminsi 14 yo gukora urugendo. Ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, mu Bushinwa, hari undi muntu umwe gusa wari umaze iminsi itanu arwaye, ari we wari uvuye i Istanbul ajya i Guangzhou.
Ku itariki ya 24 Werurwe 2020, Minisitiri w'Intebe w'u Bushinwa Li Keqiang yatangaje ko ubwandu bw'abanduye mu gihugu bwarahagaritswe ku buryo bw'ibanze, kandi ko ubwandu bwabayeho mu Bushinwa.
