Abashaka kujya mu Bushinwa bagomba gusaba viza muri ambasade cyangwa muri konsulatari y'u Bushinwa.
Guverinoma y'u Bushinwa yashishikarije ubucuruzi n'ubuhinzi kongera gufungura ku itariki ya 30 Werurwe, kandi itanga inguzanyo y'amafaranga ku bucuruzi. Inama y'igihugu yatangaje umunsi wo kwicuza, uzatangira n'ikiruhuko cy'iminsi itatu cy'igihugu ku isaha ya 10:00 ku itariki ya 4 Mata, mu gihe umunsi mukuru w'ibirori, nubwo guverinoma y'u Bushinwa yasabye imiryango gukurikiza interineti mu bikorwa byo kwirinda icyorezo cya COVID-19.
COVID-19 yemejwe ko yageze muri Koreya y'Epfo ku wa 20 Mutarama 2020 iturutse mu Bushinwa.
Ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe ubuzima cyatangaje ko ku itariki ya 20 Gashyantare habayeho kwiyongera kw'ibimenyetso by'abanduye, ahanini biturutse ku iteraniro ry'abayoboke b'idini ryitwa Shincheonji, ryabereye i Daegu.
Abenshi mu bantu bari mu idini rya Shincheonji bari baje i Daegu baturutse mu mujyi wa Wuhan, bakekwaho kuba ari bo batumye iki cyorezo cyigera.
Ku itariki ya 22 Gashyantare, mu bantu 9.336 bari mu idini, 1.261 cyangwa 13% by'abagize idini ry'Abayahudi, baragize ibimenyetso. Koreya yatangaje ko hari igihe cy'ubukonje cyageze ku itariki ya 23 Gashyantare 2020.
Ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare, abantu barenga 2,000 bamaze kwemezwa muri Koreya, ku itariki ya 29 Gashyantare, bariyongereye bagera ku 3,150.
Ibigo byose bya gisirikare bya Koreya y'Epfo byashyizwe mu kato nyuma y'uko ibipimo byerekanaga ko abasirikare batatu bari banduye virusi.
Ibihe by'indege na byo byagize ingaruka, bityo birahinduka. Koreya yazanye gahunda nini kandi nziza ku isi yo kugenzura abaturage kugira ngo babone virusi kandi bakwirakwize abanduye, ndetse no gukurikirana no gushyira mu kato abantu bagiranye ubwandu n'abanduye.
Uburyo bwo gupima, harimo gutanga raporo ku giti cyawe ku bimenyetso by'abimukira bavuye mu mahanga vuba aha binyuze kuri porogaramu kuri telefoni, gupima virusi, ku buryo byaboneka ku munsi ukurikiyeho, no kongera ubushobozi bwo gupima, bituma abantu 20,000 bapimwa buri munsi.
Porogaramu ya Koreya y'Epfo yagaragaye ko ari nziza mu guhangana n'iki cyorezo nubwo nta cyizere cy'umujyi wose. Umuryango wa Koreya y'Epfo warashyamiranye ku kuntu Perezida Moon Jae-in yabyitwayemo.
Abanyakoreya benshi bakoze inyandiko z'amahitamo abiri, urugero nko gushinja Moon ibyo bavuga ko ubutegetsi bwe butakemura ikibazo cy'indwara cyangwa kumushimira ku cyakemuwe.
Ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, Koreya y'Epfo yatangaje ko ifite umubare muto w'abanduye ku munsi ugereranyije n'uw'iminsi yose mu byumweru bine bishize.
Ku itariki ya 29 Werurwe, hari amakuru avuga ko guhera ku itariki ya 1 Mata, abimukira bashya bavuye mu mahanga bazaba bari mu kato k'ibyumweru bibiri.
Nkuko byatangajwe n'itangazamakuru ku itariki ya 1 Mata, Koreya y'Epfo yabonye ibisabwa byo gufashwa mu gupima virusi kuva mu bihugu 121 bitandukanye.
Iran yatangaje ko hari abantu babiri bamaze guhitanwa na SARS-CoV-2 ku wa 19 Gashyantare i Qom, nk'uko bivugwa na Minisiteri y'Ubuzima n'Uburezi bw'Ubuvuzi.
Ingamba za mbere leta yashyizeho zirimo guhagarika ibitaramo n'ibindi bikorwa by'umuco, imikino n'ibirori byo gusarura, kuwa gatanu no gufunga kaminuza, amashuri yisumbuye n'amashuri.
Iran yateganyije miliyari eshanu z'amadolari y'amanyamerika yo kurwanya iyi virusi.
Perezida Hassan Rouhani yavuze ko nta gahunda yo gushyira mu kato akarere kahuye n'ingaruka z'iki cyorezo, ko abantu bonyine ari bo bazaba barasiwe.
Inshingano zo kongera ingendo zo kuva mu mujyi ujya mu wundi zatangajwe muri Werurwe, nubwo ingendo z'abantu benshi zihagaze mu mujyi ujya mu wundi mbere y'iminsi mikuru y'umwaka mushya y'abaturage ba Burusiya.
Ibihangano by'Abashiya i Qom bikomeje gufungura abakora ibikorwa by'ubwoko bw'Imana kugeza ku itariki ya 16 Werurwe 2020. Irani yabaye ihuriro ry'icyorezo nyuma y'u Bushinwa mu kwezi kwa Gashyantare.
Ku bijyanye n'ibyifuzo byo gufunga icyorezo cy'indwara muri Iran, ibihugu birenga icumi byakurikiranye ibyabaye byasubiye muri Irani ku wa 28 Gashyantare, bigaragaza ko icyorezo gishobora kuba gikomeye kurusha ibyabaye 388 byatangajwe na guverinoma ya Irani kuri iyo tariki.
Inteko ishinga amategeko ya Iran yafunze, igizwe n'abadepite 23 mu 290 bivugwa ko bageze kuri iki cyorezo ku itariki ya 3 Werurwe.
Ku itariki ya 12 Werurwe, umuryango uharanira uburenganzira bwa muntu wasabye inzego zishinzwe gufunga muri Iran kurekura abarinzi b'uburenganzira bwa muntu bafungiwe mu buryo bw'ubutagondwa bagamije kurwanya mu mahoro, ndetse no kurekura imfungwa zose zifite uburenganzira bw'ikirenga ku buryo bw'agateganyo.
Bivugwa ko virusi ifite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura mu bigo byafunze nka za gereza aho hari n'uburwayi.
Ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe, guverinoma ya Irani yatangaje ko abantu 100 bapfa ku munsi, ari byo bibarirwa mu bihumbi by'abapfuye ku munsi, ari byo bibarirwa mu bihumbi by'abapfuye ku munsi umwe, ku rwego rwo hejuru mu gihugu kuva icyorezo cyatangira.
Abantu bagera kuri 12 b'abategetsi ba Irani cyangwa abahoze ari abanyapolitiki, barapfuye bazize iyi ndwara kugeza ku itariki ya 17 Werurwe.
Ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, Irani yari imaze kubona abantu bashya 50 banduye mu isaha, kandi buri minota icumi yaboneraga umuntu umwe upfa azize Coronavirus.
Nkuko byatangajwe n'ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS), mu gihugu cya Iran hari abantu bagera kuri batanu banduye kurusha abamaze kuvugwa.
Nanone kandi, cyatangaje ko ibihano Amerika yafatiye Uburayi bishobora kugira ingaruka ku bushobozi bw'igihugu bwo guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Umukuru w'umuryango w'abibumbye ushinzwe uburenganzira bwa muntu yasabye ko ibihugu byugarijwe n'icyorezo, harimo na Iran, bifatirwa ibihano by'ubukungu.
Icyorezo cy'indwara cyemejwe ko cyakwirakwiriye mu Butaliyani ku wa 31 Mutarama ubwo abashyitsi babiri b'Abashinwa bageragezaga SARS-CoV-2 i Roma.
