Ibikorwa by'ubutabazi by'indwara ya COVID-19 byagaragaraga nyuma, byatangiye ku bantu 16 bo mu ntara ya Lombardy ku wa 21 Gashyantare. Ku wa 22 Gashyantare, Minisiteri y'Intebe yatangaje itegeko rishya ryo guhagarika icyorezo, harimo no gufunga abantu barenga 50,000 baturutse mu mijyi 11 itandukanye yo mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani.
