Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) rishimiye imihati y'ubutegetsi bw'u Bushinwa mu kurwanya iki cyorezo.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryavuze ko hari itandukaniro hagati y'icyorezo cya SARS mu 2002-2004, aho abategetsi b'u Bushinwa bashinjwa guhisha ibanga ryabangamiye gahunda zo kwirinda no kugenzura imikorere y'ikibazo, n'ikibazo cy'ubu, aho guverinoma y'u Bushinwa yahaye ubufasha bwo kuvugurura gahunda yo guhangana n'ibiza mbere ya Noheri y'Umwaka w'Icyumweru.
Ku wa 23 Mutarama, mu gusubiza ku cyemezo cy'ubuyobozi bw'igihugu cyo gushyira mu bikorwa itegeko ryo guhagarika ingendo i Wuhan, uhagarariye OMS Gauden Galea yavuze ko nubwo atari byo WHO yatanze inama, ariko ko ari ikimenyetso gikomeye cy'uko biyemeje kurwanya icyorezo aho cyigaragambya cyane, cyatangaje ko icyorezo kitigeze kibaho mu mateka y'ubuzima bw'abaturage. Ku wa 30 Mutarama, nyuma y'uko abantu benshi bava mu Bushinwa bagana mu bindi bihugu, n'umubare w'abandura mu bindi bihugu bitanu, WHO yatangaje ko icyorezo cyabaye icyorezo cya mbere cy'ubwandu mu rwego rw'ubuzima rusange, cyatangiye mu mwaka wa 2009.
Umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, yavuze ko PHEIC ari yo mpamvu ishobora gukwirakwira ku isi hose, cyane cyane mu bihugu bifite amikoro make cyangwa yo hagati, nta gahunda ikomeye y'ubuzima.
"Mu gusubiza ku bikorwa by'ibihano by'ingendo, Tedros yavuze ko ""nta mpamvu yo guhagarika ingendo n'ubucuruzi mpuzamahanga bidakenewe"" kandi ko ""Umuryango w'Abibumbye wita ku buzima ntugira icyo utegeka ku bijyanye n'ingendo n'impunzi"".
"Ku wa 5 Gashyantare, OMS yasabye umuryango w'isi gutanga miliyoni 675 z'amadolari yo gutanga amafaranga yo kwitegura ibikorwa by'ingamba mu bihugu bifite amikoro make, ivuga ko byihutirwa gushyigikira ibyo bihugu bitagira uburyo bwo gushaka abantu banduye iyi virusi, nubwo byamaze gukwirakwira".
"Tedros yakomeje avuga ko ""ibihugu byose iyo hari umunyagoyagoya, bigereranya abafite ubukene bose"" kandi asaba umuryango mpuzamahanga ko ""guhora ubu nta cyo bivuze ejo hazaza". Mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru cyo ku wa 11 Gashyantare, OMS yise iki cyorezo COVID-19".
Umunsi umwe, Tedros yemeje ko Umunyamabanga Mukuru wa ONU, António Guterres, yemeye guha ububasha bw'ikigo cyose cya ONU mu gusubiza.
"Ibigo by'Umuryango w'Abibumbye byo kugenzura ibibazo by'ingorane byashyizwe mu bikorwa, bigatuma habaho guhuza ibisubizo by'Umuryango w'Abibumbye byose, aho Umuryango w'Abibumbye wita ku buzima uzemerera abantu kwita cyane ku buzima, mu gihe ibindi bigo bishobora gutanga ubuhanga bwabo mu gushyigikira imibereho y'abaturage n'ubukungu n'ingaruka z'ibiterambere ry'icyorezo""".
Ku itariki ya 14 Gashyantare, itsinda ry'inteko ishinga amategeko ya OMS, rifatanyije n'u Bushinwa, ryashyizweho kugira ngo rihe impuguke mpuzamahanga n'umuryango w'abibumbye imimerere yo mu Bushinwa, rifashe mu kurwanya indwara zo mu karere no gusuzuma ubukana n'ubushobozi bwo kwandura iyi ndwara, rihagarike amasomo n'inama n'ibigo by'ingamba by'igihugu by'ingenzi, kandi rihagarike ingendo zo kumenya ingaruka z'ingamba zo gusubiza ku rwego rw'intara n'akarere, harimo n'abantu n'abatuye mu karere. Ku itariki ya 25 Gashyantare, OMS yatangaje ko hari ingamba nyinshi zikwiye gushyirwaho kugira ngo ibihugu byose bitegure icyorezo, kuko byumva ko icyorezo kizacyugarije mu gihe kiza.
Mu gusubiza ku buryo icyorezo cyugarije Iran, OMS yohereje itsinda ry'imiryango muri icyo gihugu kugira ngo rigenzure uko ibintu byifashe. Ku wa 28 Gashyantare, abayobozi b'umuryango w'abibumbye ku buzima bavuze ko ibipimo by'iterabwoba rya Coronavirus ku rwego rw'isi bizongerwaho ku gipimo cyo hejuru cyane, ku rwego rwo ku rwego rwo hejuru rw'ubwitonzi n'ubushakashatsi.
Mike Ryan, umuyobozi wa WHO mu bikorwa by'ubutabazi, yavuze ko iyi ari yo myumvire y'ibibera ku butegetsi bwose ku isi: "Nimuhaguruke".
"Virus ishobora kuba igiye kuza, bityo rero ugomba kwitegura, ugakomeza kwemeza ko uburyo bukwiriye bwo gusubiza bishobora gufasha isi kwirinda ingaruka mbi cyane".
