Icyorezo cya Coronavirus cyakwirakwijwe n'impamvu zitandukanye, urugero nk'ibura ry'ibikoresho, gukoresha ibikoresho mu kurwanya indwara, guhaha mu bwoba no mu bibazo, inganda n'ibikorwaremezo, gutwara abantu ku isi hose.
