Muri Australia, icyorezo cyatumye abacuruzi basanzwe babona uburyo bushya bwo kugurisha ibicuruzwa byabo mu Bushinwa.
Iyi myigaragambyo yatumye haba ikibazo cy'amata, amata, abana mu masoko, nyuma y'aho Leta ya Australia ikabitsinda. Nubwo ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bwiyongereye mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani no mu ntara ya Wuhan, kandi ko ibisabwa mu by'ibiribwa bikomeje kwiyongera, ibi bice byombi byakijijwe ikibazo cy'ubukene bukomeye.
Ingamba z'u Bushinwa n'u Butaliyani zo kurwanya ubucuruzi bw'ibikomoka ku bidakoreshwa mu buryo bwemewe n'amategeko n'amategeko zagize icyo zigeraho mu kwirinda inzara y'ibiribwa bitoshye byitezwe mu Burayi no muri Amerika ya Ruguru.
Mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani, umusaruro w'ibikomoka ku buhinzi ntiwagabanutse cyane, ariko ibiciro bishobora kuzamuka, nk'uko abahagarariye inganda babivuga.
