Icyorezo cya Coronavirus gishobora gutwara imirimo miliyoni 47 muri Amerika, kandi igipimo cy'abatarimo akazi gishobora kuzamuka kigera kuri 32%, nk'uko byemezwa na Federal Reserve Bank of St. Louis. Gucumbikira mu rugo mu Buhinde byahitanye abakozi b'Abanyarwanda bagera kuri miliyoni icumi (aho bahembwa buri munsi). Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ikigo Angus Reid Institute bwagaragaje ko imiryango yo muri Canada 44% yagize ikibazo cy'ubushomeri. Abakozi bagera ku 900,000 muri Esipanye batakaje akazi kabo kuva igihugu cyashyiraho itegeko ryo kuguma mu rugo mu kwezi kwa gatatu 2020.
Mu kwezi kwa gatatu, abakozi 4 miliyoni bo mu Bufaransa basabye inguzanyo y'ubushomeri bw'agateganyo, naho abakozi 1 miliyoni bo mu Bwongereza basabye inguzanyo rusange.
