Urugero, ahantu ho gukaraba intoki mu turere twinshi tw'ibirwa byo muri Afurika, hafi y'aho abantu bakorera ubwabo n'aho bakirira abantu bose, usanga ari gake cyane, nubwo haba hari uburyo buhenze bwo kubaka aho gukaraba intoki.
Ariko kandi, ibipimo by'ubutabogama bw'amaboko bishobora guterwa n'uko umuntu adakora neza, aho guterwa n'ikibazo cyo kubura amazi cyangwa isabune.
Gushyigikira no gushyigikira isuku y'amaboko n'isabune bishobora kugira ingaruka ku cyemezo cy'ingamba, bigatuma abantu bamenya akamaro ko gusukura intoki, kandi bigatuma abantu bagira ihinduka mu myifatire mu gihe kirekire.
Kugira ngo ibyo bikorwa bikorwe neza, igenzura n'igishoro ni ngombwa.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bushakashatsi 70 bwagaragaje ko uburyo bwo mu muryango bwagaragaje ko bwemewe mu kongera ubwiherero bw'amaboko mu bigo by'amashuri by'imyororokere, mu gihe ubukangurambaga bw'imikorere ya sosiyete bw'abantu bwo mu rwego rw'ubucuruzi bw'amashuri bwagaragaje ko budakora. Urugero rumwe mu byatewe n'uko byatewe n'ishyirahamwe UNICEF, rwagaragaje ko gushishikariza amashuri gukurikiza ingamba zoroheje kandi z'agaciro gake kugira ngo abanyeshuri bihatire gukaraba intoki mu gihe bafite isabune, mu bindi bisobanuro.
Iyo ibipimo by'ibanze byuzuwe, ishuri rishobora guhinduka rikava ku nyenyeri imwe rikajya ku nyenyeri eshatu.
Kubaka ahantu ho gukaraba intoki ku bwinshi ni kimwe mu bigize gahunda yo guteza imbere gukaraba intoki, bigatuma indwara zitandura n'urupfu rw'abana bigabanuka.
Gushyiraho amaboko ku isi hose ni urugero rw'ibikorwa byo guteza imbere ubushishozi, bigerageza kugera ku mpinduka mu myifatire. Nyuma y'icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019-20, UNICEF yashyize imbaraga mu gushyiraho ikimenyetso cy'ibyiyumvo cyo gukaraba intoki.
Ubushakashatsi buke bwakozwe ku bijyanye n'igiciro cy'amafaranga y'imyenda yo gukaraba intoki mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, bufitanye isano n'ibipimo bya DALY.
Ariko ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko gushishikariza abantu gukaraba intoki bakoresheje isabune byatwaraga amafaranga make ugereranyije n'ayandi mafaranga y'isuku n'amazi.
Icy'ingenzi cyo gukaraba intoki ni uko ubuzima bw'abantu, cyane cyane ku bantu bari mu mimerere igoranye, urugero nk'ababyeyi babyaye cyangwa abasirikare bakomeretse mu bitaro, bwa mbere bwamenyekanye mu kinyejana cya 19 hagati n'abahanga babiri mu kuvura intoki: Ignaz Semmelweis, umuganga wo muri Hongiriya wakoreraga i Vienne, muri Otirishiya, na Florence Nightingale, Umwongereza washinze ubuforomokazi bwa none.
Icyo gihe abantu benshi bari bakizera ko indwara ziterwa n'umuti mubi witwa miasmas.
Mu myaka ya 1980, icyorezo cy'indwara z'imirire n'indwara z'uburwayi byatumye Ibitaro byo muri Amerika byo Genzura no Gukumira Indwara byitoza guteza imbere isuku y'amaboko, bikaba ari uburyo bw'ingenzi bwo kwirinda kwandura.
Nyuma y'icyorezo cy'indwara ya Sida y'Ingurube mu 2009 n'icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyakwirakwiriye ku isi hose mu 2020, ibihugu bimwe na bimwe byamenye ko gukaraba intoki n'isabune ari ingenzi mu kwirinda indwara.
Urugero, amashusho arimo amagambo ngo "kwambara neza intoki" (technical hand wash) (kugeza mu gihe umuntu yiyuhagira) ashyirwa mu byumba by'imyenda mu biraro rusange no mu biraro by'amazu y'ibiro n'indege mu Budage.
Kuvuga ngo gukaraba intoki kugira ngo ukureho ikintu, bisobanura ko utemera ko ikintu runaka kigomba gukorwa cyangwa ko udashaka ko hagira ikintu runaka kigomba gukorwa.
Ryaturutse ku murongo wo muri Bibiliya wo muri Matayo aho Ponsiyo Pilato yahanaguye umwanzuro wo kubamba Yesu Kristo, ariko rihinduka ijambo rikoreshwa cyane mu mico imwe n'imwe y'Abongereza.
Umunyamakuru wa BBC avuga ko umugore we w'umunyamwete mu by'ubucuruzi, ari we Marguerite, yigeze gufatwa n'umugabo we, ndetse ko yari afite ikibazo cy'ubusambanyi.
Basanze abantu bamaze kwibuka cyangwa gutekereza ku bikorwa by'ubwiyandarike, bahita batekereza ko bagomba gukaraba intoki kenshi kurusha abandi, kandi bagatanga agaciro kenshi ku bikoresho byo gukaraba intoki.
Byongeye kandi, abantu bemerewe gukaraba intoki nyuma yo gukora ibyo bikorwa byo gutekereza, birashoboka ko batagira uruhare mu "kwisukura, kwihana" cyangwa ibindi bikorwa byo gukosora nk'uko abigenga babigenza.
Hari amadini avuga ko gukaraba intoki ari ukugira ngo umuntu agire isuku n'ibindi bisobanuro. Ikimenyetso cyo gukaraba intoki ukoresheje amazi ariko udakoresheje sabuni, ni kimwe mu bintu by'ingenzi by'ingenzi mu gukaraba intoki mu madini amwe n'amwe, harimo Ababahá'í, Abahindu, tevilah na netilat yadayim mu idini rya Yuda, Lavabo mu idini rya Gikristo, na Wudhu mu idini rya Isilamu. Amadini yose avuga ko gukaraba intoki ari ngombwa cyane nyuma y'ibikorwa runaka.
