Gutegeka impanuka mu kazi ku ndwara ya COVID-19
Gufata nabi akazi ku COVID-19 ni ugushyira mu bikorwa ingamba z'umutekano n'ubuzima ku kazi mu rwego rwo gucunga ibyago byo kwirinda icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Gusuzuma akaga mu kazi, ku kazi no ku kazi, bishingiye ku cyemezo cy'ibyago by'ibyago, aho indwara ivuye, uburemere bw'indwara mu baturage n'ingaruka z'uko buri mukozi ashobora kwandura COVID-19.
Nkuko bivugwa na US Occupational Safety and Health Administration (OSHA). Abakozi bafite ibyago bike cyane, nta mishyikirano myiza bagirana n'abaturage n'abandi bakozi, bagirwa inama yo gukoresha ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda kwandura, harimo gukaraba intoki, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, guhumeka no gukomeza isuku n'ubwandu bw'ibidukikije.
Imirimo igenda ihura n'akaga gakomeye cyane, harimo abantu bakenera guhura kenshi cyangwa kuba hafi y'abantu batazi cyangwa bakeka ko bafite COVID-19, ariko bashobora kwandura kubera ko ubwandu bw'umuryango bukomeje kubaho cyangwa ingendo mpuzamahanga.
Ibyo birimo abakozi bagirana n'abaturage muri rusange, nk'uko bimeze ku mashuri y'ibidukikije, ibigo by'ubwibone n'ibigo bimwe na bimwe by'ubucuruzi.
Ubuyobozi bw'iki kigo bufite ingamba zo kwirinda indwara z'ubwandu, harimo guhumeka mu buryo bw'umwuka, kwirinda gusama, no kugira ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi biboneka mu gihe hagize umuntu uhura na COVID-19.
OSHA ivuga ko abakozi b'ubuvuzi n'ahantu h'ihamba bamenyekanye cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19 bafite ibyago byinshi byo guhura n'abantu ku giti cyabo, bigatuma bagira ibyago byinshi iyo abakozi bashyizeho gahunda yo gukora icyemezo cy'ubuvuzi cyangwa bakusanya cyangwa bakura ibipimo by'abantu bamenyekanye cyangwa bakekwaho ko bafite COVID-19.
Gufata nabi abo bakozi bikubiyemo gucunga ingufu z'ubuhanga nk'ibyumba by'umuyaga byugarijwe nabi, n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bihuye n'akazi.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 gishobora kugira ingaruka ku kazi.
Abakozi bashobora kuba batajya ku kazi kubera ko barwaye, ko bakeneye kwita ku bandi cyangwa kubera ko batinya ko bashobora guhura n'ibibazo.
Ubucuruzi bushobora guhinduka haba mu bijyanye n'ibyo ibicuruzwa bifuza ndetse n'uburyo bwo kubikuraho (nk'uko kugenda mu modoka ku masaha y'ikirenga cyangwa mu modoka cyangwa serivisi zo gutwara).
Amaherezo, ingendo z'ibintu ziva mu turere tw'isi twahuye n'icyorezo cya Covid-19 zahagaritswe. Ingamba zo guhangana n'icyorezo no guhangana nacyo zishobora gukoreshwa mu gutanga ubuyobozi ku bikorwa byo kwirinda.
Gahunda yo guhangana n'ibigeragezo bijyanye n'akazi n'akazi, harimo inkomoko y'ibyago, ibyago biterwa no gushinga inzu n'abaturage, ndetse n'ibyago by'umukozi umwe ku giti cye, urugero nk'iza bukuru cyangwa indwara z'amagara.
Nanone kandi, bagaragaje uburyo bwo kugenzura ibyo bintu bishobora guteza akaga, kandi bateganya uko ibintu bizagenda mu gihe hazabaho icyorezo.
Gutegura no guhangana n'icyorezo bishobora kuba ari igikorwa cy'ubwoko cyangwa cy'ubwoko.
Intego zo guhangana n'icyo cyorezo zirimo kugabanya ibyo abakozi bakora, kwirinda abantu bafite ibyago byinshi byo kugira ingaruka mbi ku buzima, gukomeza ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi no kugabanya ingaruka mbi ku zindi nzego mu miterere yabo yo gutanga.
Icyorezo cyugarije abaturage ni uko ubucuruzi bwo mu karere kahuye n'iki cyorezo bwitabiriye.
Ubuyobozi bw'ibiza ni urwego rukoreshwa cyane mu by'umutekano mu kazi no mu buzima bw'abantu kugira ngo bagenzure neza ibyago by'itsinda.
Mu gihe icyorezo cya COVID-19 kidashobora gukurwaho, uburyo bwiza cyane bwo kugenzura ni ubuhanga, hanyuma ni ubuyobozi n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi.
Ubuyobozi bw'ubuhinzi burimo gukinga abakozi bakava mu kaga k'akazi, nta gushingiye ku myitwarire y'abakozi, kandi bushobora kuba umuti usanzwe ukoreshwa cyane.
Ubuyobozi bw'ubuyobozi ni ihinduka ry'amahame cyangwa uburyo bwo gukora bukenera ibikorwa by'abakozi, abakozi cyangwa abakozi.
Ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi (PPE) byitwa ko bidafite ubushobozi bwo gucunga ingufu mu by'ubugenzuzi no mu by'ubutegetsi, ariko bishobora gufasha kwirinda ibibazo bimwe na bimwe.
Buri bwoko bwa PPE bugomba gutorwa hashingiwe ku kaga kabyo ku bakozi, abakozi bagomba kuba bashyizwe neza uko bishoboka kose (urugero nk'ibikoresho byo guhumeka), bambaye neza kandi bakagenzurwa buri gihe, bagasubirwamo kandi bagasubirwamo igihe cyose bikenewe, kandi bakurwaho neza, bakagezwa neza, bakagumana cyangwa bakajugunywa mu kato kugira ngo birinde kwandura.
Nkuko bivugwa na US Occupational Safety and Health Administration (OSHA), abakozi bafite ibyago bike cyane nta mishyikirano myiza bagirana n'abaturage n'abandi bakozi.
Ingamba zo kwirinda kwandura zafashwe mu kazi zirimo gukaraba intoki kenshi no guhanagura intoki, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, guhumeka, gusinzira, gutanga imyanda, guhanagura, gutegura telefoni cyangwa guhindurira abandi ibikoresho, kwirinda gukoresha ibikoresho n'ibikoresho by'abandi, no gukomeza isuku n'ubwandu busanzwe bw'aho bakorera.
Kugaragariza abantu ubwandu n'ubwirinzi ni intambwe ikomeye mu kurinda abakozi, abakiriya, abashyitsi n'abandi mu kazi.
Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara zandura (CDC) gisaba ko abakozi bafite ibimenyetso by'indwara zikomeye zo mu mutwe bagomba kuguma mu rugo kugeza igihe bazaba badafite umuriro, umuriro n'ibindi bimenyetso by'indwara, nibura amasaha 24 badafite imiti yo kugabanya ubukana cyangwa imiti yo guhindurira ibimenyetso, kandi amategeko yo kuruhuka kubera indwara ni ay'ubushakashatsi, yemerera abakozi kuguma mu rugo kwita ku bagize umuryango barwaye, kandi abakozi bagomba kumenya ayo mahame.
