Iyo umuntu arwaye mu ndege, igenzura rikwiye kugira ngo rikingire abakozi n'abandi bantu, rigizwe no gutandukanya abarwayi n'abandi ku birometero 6 by'ubugari, rigatuma umwe mu bagize umuryango ashakira abarwayi serivisi, agaha abarwayi amavuta, cyangwa agasaba abarwayi guhosha akanwa n'inzirakarengane mu gihe bahunga cyangwa bahunga.
Abagenzi bagombye kwambara imyenda y'ubuvuzi bashobora kuyisiga nyuma yo kuyikoresha mu gihe bita ku bagenzi barwaye cyangwa bafite ubumuga ku mubiri, kandi bashobora kuba bafite ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi by'inyongera niba mu rugendo hari umuriro, guhinda umushyitsi cyangwa guhumeka nabi.
Ibikoresho by'amaboko n'ibindi bintu byajugunywa bigomba kujugunywa mu mifuka y'ibinyabuzima, kandi ibifite ubumara bigomba gukorerwa isuku no kwanduzwa. Ku byo gutwara abantu, harimo n'amato n'izindi mato, kugenzura impanuka birimo gutinda urugendo igihe urwaye, no kwiherera, no kubimenyesha ikigo cy'ubuvuzi cyo mu ndege byihutirwa niba umuntu afite ubushyuhe cyangwa indi ndwara igihe ari ku rugendo.
Urugero, gukurikirana kwa muganga byagombye kuba mu cyumba cy'umuntu ku giti cye. Ku mashuri n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi CDC irasaba ko hakorwa igihe gito cyo gusukura cyangwa kwitsamura umuntu urwaye virusi mu kigo cy'ishuri, hatitawe ku gukwirakwira mu baturage.
Iyo hari gahunda nto cyane yo gutumiza abaturage, ingamba z'imibereho myiza zishobora gukurikizwa, urugero nko guhagarika ingendo zo mu kibuga, inama n'ibindi bikorwa bikomeye, urugero nk'imyitozo, amakipe y'abahanzi cyangwa amafunguro mu kafe, kongera intera hagati y'ameza, kuza no kwirukanwa mu buryo butunguranye, gushyiraho umubare w'abashyitsi batagikenewe no gukoresha icyicaro cy'uburwayi cyihariye ku bana bafite ibimenyetso nk'icyorezo cy'ibicurane.
Iyo hari imodoka nyinshi mu baturage, uretse ingamba zo kubungabunga abaturage, ingendo z'amashuri ziganje zishobora gutekerezwaho. Ku bakozi bashinzwe gukurikiza amategeko bakora ibikorwa bya buri munsi vuba, CDC ibona ko ari byo bigira ingaruka mbi ku buzima bwabo.
