Ingirabuzima fatizo (ACE2) ni ingirabuzima fatizo ibamo ingirabuzima fatizo z'ibihaha, umutima, impyiko n'inda.
ACE2 irwanya ingirabuzima fatizo ya acetone (ACE), igaragaza ko igabanya ingirabuzima fatizo ya acetone-II kandi ikongera angon (Angon) 1-7) bigatuma iba umuti ushimishije mu kuvura indwara z'umutima. ACE2 kandi ikora nk'ikirere cyo kwinjira mu ngirabuzima fatizo zimwe na zimwe za coronavirus.
Ingirabuzima fatizo z'umuntu ni zimwe mu zikunze kwitwa hACE2.
Inchotensin-2 ikora ingirabuzima fatizo, ni ingirabuzima fatizo irimo ibyuma biboneka ku gice cy'ubutaka cy'ingirabuzima fatizo n'ibindi bice by'umubiri.
Ingirabuzimafatizo ACE2 irimo n'umwanya wa N-terminal peptidase M2 domain n'umurongo w'umushyikirizi wa acide ku buryo bw'umushinga wa C-terminal.
ACE2 ni inzira ya kabiri y'ubwoko bwa I bw'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima, ingirabuzimafatizo zayo zikora ibijyanye n'ubutaka bw'ingirabuzimafatizo z'ibihaha n'izindi.
Ingingo z'inyongera za ACE2 zisohorwa mu ngendo z'ingenzi z'indi enzyme izwi nka cedes, igice cy'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima cyasenyutse gihita gisohorwa mu maraso, amaherezo gihita gisohorwa mu mpyiko.
ACE2 iboneka mu mibiri myinshi: ACE2 ifitanye isano n'ingirabuzimafatizo z'ingirabuzimafatizo z'ingenzi z'ubwoko bwa II, impyiko, ingirabuzimafatizo z'amaraso mato, intoki n'intoki, ndetse n'ingirabuzimafatizo z'amaraso z'ibinyabuzima byinshi.
ACE2 mRNA kandi iboneka mu bice by'inyuma by'ubwonko bw'intanga, mu gice cy'ibanze cy'ibere, no mu bice by'ubwonko.
Icy'ingenzi cya ACE2 ni uko gifasha mu guhangana n'ingaruka za ACE.
ACE ihindura ingirabuzima fatizo ya angiotensin I mu maraso, igatuma ingirabuzima fatizo ya angiotensin II ihinduka ingirabuzima fatizo ya angiotensin.
ACE2 itandukanya amino acid carboxyl-terminal amino (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) n'andi ariyo angitoentensin (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) maze ikajya mu bwoko bw'umurava w'umurava w'umurava (vasodilator angiotensin) (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 ishobora no kwica izindi peptide zimwe na zimwe, harimo [des-Arg9] - bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A na ghrelin.
ACE2 ifasha mu guhagarika ingufu za SLC6A19 zitanga amino acids, kandi bigaragara mu ndwara ya Hartnup.
Kubera ko hari poroteyine ihita ikora mu gice cy'umubiri cy'umubiri cy'umubiri, ACE2 ikora nk'ikirindiro cy'ingenzi mu ngirabuzimafatizo z'indwara zimwe na zimwe zandura, harimo HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virusi ituma umuntu arwara SARS) na SARS-CoV-2 (virusi ituma umuntu arwara COVID-19).
Byongeye kandi, biragaragara ko ingirabuzimafatizo za S1 za SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV2 zinyura mu ngirabuzimafatizo ACE2 ziboneka ku ngirabuzimafatizo, bigaterwa no gutandukanya virusi na za enzyme mu duce tw'ingirabuzimafatizo.
Iyi gahunda yo kwinjiza kandi igasaba ko poroteyine ya S igenda yifashishwa mu gutangiza ingirabuzimafatizo ya TMPRSS2 mu mubiri, ubuhinga bwo kwihagarika buri gukorwaho ubushakashatsi ni uburyo bwo kuvura.
Icyakora, hari inzobere mu by'imibereho y'abantu n'inzego zikomeza gutanga inama zo gukomeza gukoresha imiti itera SIDA n'iyo kwivuza.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ikigo cy'ubuvuzi n'ubuvanganzo, bwashyizwe ahagaragara ku itariki ya 11 Nyakanga 2012, bwagaragaje ko gukoresha imiti itera ubukana bwa ACE byibanda kugabanukaho 34% by'ibyago byo kurwara indwara y'ibihaha ugereranyije n'abatayifite.
Icyakora, ibyago byo kurwara indwara y'ibihaha byagabanutse ku barwayi bavurwa bakoresheje imiti itera SIDA (ACE inhibitors), ariko bari bafite ibyago byo kurwara ibihaha, cyane cyane ku barwayi bavunitse mu bwonko no ku mutima.
Gukoresha imiti itera SIDA (ACE) byashyizwe hamwe no kugabanya uburwayi bw'impyiko, nubwo ingaruka z'iyo miti zitari nyinshi cyane kurusha ibyago byo kurwara impyiko.
Gufata imiti ya ACE2 (rhACE2) byitwa ko ari umuti w'indwara y'ibihaha, kandi bituma amaraso akomeza gutembera mu bihimba by'umutima, ndetse bigatuma umwuka utembera cyane, bigatuma habaho indwara zikomeye z'ubuhumekero.
Igice cy'ubuzima cya rhACE2 mu muntu ni amasaha 10, kandi intangiriro y'ibikorwa ni iminota 30 y'inyongera ku gihe cy'akazi (igihe) cy'amasaha 24.
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko rhACE2 ishobora kuba umuti ugira ingaruka nziza ku bantu batagihanganira indwara zisanzwe z'ingwara ya RAS cyangwa mu barwayi bafite ingendo z'ingwara z'ingwara z'ingwara z'ingwara z'ingwara z'ingwara z'ingwara z'ingwara z'ingwara z'ingwara z'ingwara z'ingurube. RhACE2 yatanzwe yagenzuwe mu igeragezwa ry'ubuvuzi mu kuvura ibimenyetso bikomeye by'ingwara z'ingwara z'ingwara.
